BFN 

  [Text] Patriarch Aleksiy of Moscow and all of Russia and 
Serbian Patriarch Pavle are going to visit the republic of 
Srpska, where they will visit the seat of the Davro-Bosnian 
metropolitan in Sokolac and talk to Metropolitan Nikolaj. The 
ecclesiastical dignitaries will hold talks in Pale with the 
leadership of the republic of Srpska, including President 
Radovan Karadzic. A visit with Russian members of the UN 
Protection Force in the Sarajevo Serbian settlement of Grbavica 
is scheduled to take place afterwards. The Russian and Serbian 
patriarchs are supposed to meet with Zagreb Cardinal Franjo 
Kuharic and Reis-ul-Ulema Mustafa Ceric at Sarajevo airport. It 
is planned that Patriarchs Aleksiy II and Pavle, together with 
Russian and Serbian bishops, will bless the land on which the 
Serbian Orthodox Church will be built. 

